snippet.title: [c64] Fast Eddie (1982)
snippet.description:
I completed the first loop and about half from the second (reaching difficulty level 4). Difficulty is increased by one notch for every half loops. Max beginning difficulty is 8 so I believe 9 would be the actual maximum difficulty.

It's not a spectacular game, but it holds some nostalgia value for me. This will be the last game I'm going to upload from 1982.

Publisher: Sirius Software

http://www.lemon64.com/games/details.php?ID=893
